OL,6,FIt would almost certainly mean more
OL,7,Fcuts which people would actually
OL,8,Fnotice.
OL,10,FIt's time for those of us who care
OL,11,Fabout the BBC to make it clear that
OL,12,Fwe would be prepared to pay for an
OL,13,Finflationary rise in the TV licence.
OL,15,FThe only people who want the BBC
OL,16,Fseriously reduced in scale and scope
OL,17,Fare the people who oppose it on
OL,18,Fideological or dogmatic grounds.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/7
