OL,3,CMore difficult decisions ahead for
OL,4,Cthe BBC
OL,6,FIt's a quality daytime magazine,
OL,7,Fquietly created, in the best
OL,8,Ftraditions of Pebble Mill at One,
OL,9,FAfternoon Plus and, yes, This Morning
OL,10,Fbefore it became celebrity obsessed.
OL,12,FToday came the welcome news it will
OL,13,Fbe extended by half an hour in
OL,14,FJanuary.
OL,16,FTogether with the extension of
OL,17,FBreakfast to 9.30am, it will give BBC
OL,18,FOne's morning schedule a greater
OL,19,Ffocus on live output.
